{"version":1,"content":"<html><body><p>據悉，男嬰為非華裔。警方正其暈倒原因，初步相信事件無可疑。</p><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260418/1122172007664848896015498.jpeg/cxOt5YcLz6Ye3j_8ThvO92LJiVNgpx89xZ5eGMWeXhg\" alt=\"男嬰被送往瑪嘉烈醫院治理後恢復清醒。（資料圖片）\"><figcaption>男嬰被送往瑪嘉烈醫院治理後恢復清醒。（資料圖片）</figcaption></figure></body></html>","scraped_at":"2026-05-02T22:57:32.002485+00:00","quality":{"score":0,"chars":54,"images":1,"source":"HK01 突發","fallback":"none"}}